# Flatpaks to install on first boot.
# One flatpak ID per line. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
# Processed at build time by run-component.sh: each component's
# flatpaks.list is concatenated into /usr/share/falcos/default-flatpaks
# and installed by the flatpak component's first-boot service.
io.github.kolunmi.Bazaar
